Paul George On Potential Trade To Lakers: &lsquo;I Would Love To Go Back Home And Play For My City&rsquo;<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I have no regrets at all. All that was said was a destination I would have loved to go to. There wasn&rsquo;t a gun pointed to the head, &ldquo;hey, send me here.&rdquo; I just stated somewhere I wanted to go play. You ask 87 percent of guys in the league if they would love to go back home and play for their city, play for their home. That&rsquo;s all that I stated, that I would love to go back home and play for my city.&rdquo;

